response.overview: Dartmoor "ENJOY" is one of the biggest dirt/street/slopestyle bike movie projects in Poland. A sum of 14 riders - the Dartmoor team (mostly Polish riders but also some from the Czech Republic and Russia) and some friends. The footage was filmed 2009, all year long, featuring a lot of many sessions and contests in Poland, Czech Republic, Germany, Austria and Russia. So ENJOY!
response.title: Enjoy
